headline: Has the Market Mispriced CF Industries After Its Recent Share Price Pullback?
summary: Wondering if CF Industries Holdings is quietly turning into a value opportunity, or if the market already has it priced just right? Let us walk through what the numbers are really saying about this fertilizer giant. The stock has slipped in the medium term, down 6.6% over the last month and 7.7% year to date. It is still 9.4% lower than a year ago, despite being up an impressive 134.6% over 5 years. Those swings come against a backdrop of shifting fertilizer demand and natural gas costs, as...
